data.description: Welcome to your new home! This stunning residence boasts an impeccable condition and offers a lifestyle of comfort and convenience. It is situated in close proximity to Fort Cavazos, schools, restaurants, and shopping. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the thoughtful design and layout of this home. The living room boasts a beautiful fireplace and high ceilings, creating a warm and welcoming ambiance. The well-appointed kitchen features top-of-the-line appliances and plenty of storage and counter space. Your master bedroom is located on the lower level, offering a serene retreat and easy accessibility. It boasts a generous layout and an ensuite bathroom that exudes a spa-like elegance. Outside, your backyard features a convenient shed for additional storage. Don’t miss the opportunity to make this remarkable property your own. Contact us today to schedule your viewing!
